{"tid":295167,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（賜酒）請教寫cv 關於experience問題","createTime":"2017-06-23T14:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T11:17:11.000Z","uid":10872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1eecd25c4c10e1c29ef16f190ebe52b04fd9921b","tid":295167,"uid":10872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:04:46.000Z","msg":"寫CV experience 既時候遇到一個問題<br />\n<br />\n因為以前做過一個大公司旗下既細公司<br />\n咁間大公司旗下都有幾間細公司係佢member黎<br />\n間細公司係完全唔出名無人識 聽落你會以為佢係startup 但係間母公司就好出名<br />\n咁小弟搵工都好驚cv如果就話做過間細公司，hr班老閪一見到唔識個brand就直接當我個experience廢左 <br />\n例如做過ViuTv，但佢係PCCW既其中一個，但就咁講Viutv可能無人識<br />\n我CV想靚仔d 可唔可以寫 PCCW (ViuTv) <br />\n<br />\n咁當然Viutv個個都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以我係依到只係假設Viutv無人識<br />\n<br />\n而佢reference letter都係就咁出細公司名，無間母公司名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28eef30ea4a6dc4f3fde99654c36e6db6b4fad58","tid":295167,"uid":10872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150f941bf0db5afaf2abd754cd721aae2e7974e8","tid":295167,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:26:05.000Z","msg":"你咪寫多句(Member/Subsidiary of XXXXXXX)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bac55d6ac7100a671236ce5fc2032cfffc1ccf","tid":295167,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪寫多句(Member/Subsidiary of XXXXXXX)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bl